Fantastic entry! I really enjoyed something weird but not threatening all life as we know it.

Teenagers entering the abandoned amusement park? It's believable but I immediately thought of Scooby Doo. It won't make or break this article, but I'd recommend changing that to something else, such as real estate developers or amateur local historians.

